Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.47,0:16:43.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往事前跟克劳德定好的汇合地点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.33,0:16:48.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去看看情况  你们就在那边的小屋里等我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.29,0:16:50.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席琳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.72,0:16:54.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿不了枪的你跟来也只会拖后腿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.79,0:16:56.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就照顾好孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.34,0:17:04.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽娜  我…卡塔隆在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.86,0:17:26.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:32.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.72,0:17:40.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了夺回路易丝  我会进行我的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:54.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩丽丝中尉在Celestial Being…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.86,0:17:59.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲到底从什么时候起就背叛军队了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.46,0:18:07.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈…沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.22,0:18:13.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准尉  你无法斩断思念吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.01,0:18:19.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就由我来完成吧  你的期望  你的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.54,0:18:27.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS被击落一半以上  李拜巴尔上尉被敌人俘虏？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.90,0:18:31.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传闻拥有特许的人  也名不副实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.82,0:18:34.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还不明白啊  我们的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.02,0:18:36.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是就落得这副德行？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:41.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一次作战  就只由我们出击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.31,0:18:44.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  夸下海口了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:47.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就让我期待你们的战果吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.14,0:18:49.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.56,0:18:57.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来晚了  这家伙就是改革者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.79,0:18:59.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  无庸置疑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.26,0:19:01.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能请你摘下头盔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.88,0:19:13.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸会  Celestial Being的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.27,0:19:18.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫李维夫·李拜巴尔  是改革者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.67,0:19:21.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能请你谈谈关于改革者的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.67,0:19:24.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚琉…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.67,0:19:31.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？亚琉  航向偏离预定方向了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.43,0:19:33.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修正一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.39,0:19:39.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚琉！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:40.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利塔娜小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.34,0:19:42.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.33,0:19:44.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.78,0:19:47.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还用问吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.44,0:19:53.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为  我可是改革者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.93,0:21:32.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OO Gundam  只有我才适合
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.12,0:21:35.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也这么认为吧  李杰尼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.77,0:21:37.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了  利冯兹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.33,0:21:40.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  尽说些违心的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.43,0:21:49.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普特利麦奥斯还没有联络吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.21,0:21:51.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.61,0:21:52.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.66,0:21:56.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能将吠陀的位置告知Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.36,0:22:00.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该就能打乱改革者的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.99,0:22:02.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是世界就又能…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.20,0:22:04.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.38,0:22:06.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.49,0:22:09.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰的操舵…失灵了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.22,0:22:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况有异常
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.86,0:22:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.97,0:22:15.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还不清楚  但系统全都被删除
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.31,0:22:17.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.72,0:22:20.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道  是吠陀的介入？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.83,0:22:26.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你淘气过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.15,0:22:31.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再擅自行事的话  你心里有数吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.72,0:22:36.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全无法控制了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.52,0:22:38.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脱离吧  做好小型艇的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.97,0:22:41.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  本舰的所有系统都没有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.26,0:22:44.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.55,0:22:45.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜·崔尼蒂？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.64,0:22:48.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听我说  这艘舰的系统失灵了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.65,0:22:49.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮帮我们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.20,0:22:54.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  这种事我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.47,0:22:56.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为就是我干的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.65,0:22:57.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.09,0:22:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屏幕…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.95,0:23:01.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.87,0:23:08.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手里什么都有  却还想要更多
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.48,0:23:12.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且内在还空空如也
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.18,0:23:14.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.75,0:23:19.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都讨厌这样的你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.60,0:23:23.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.20,0:23:25.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.99,0:23:36.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我要给世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.38,0:23:38.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留美！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.28,0:23:40.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…带来变革…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.84,0:23:47.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽！真受不了！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.44,0:24:04.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为改革者而觉醒的亚琉  企图抢夺OO
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.47,0:24:07.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  「亚琉·利塔娜」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.47,0:24:07.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(380,356)\fs22}A New Return
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.43,0:24:12.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该回到故乡  还是回到所爱的男人的身边
